<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="b1939_04_03_an_SraffaPiero"><teiHeader><fileDesc> <titleStmt> <title>Von <persName key="WittgensteinLudwig" role="sender" full="yes">Ludwig Wittgenstein</persName> an <persName key="SraffaPiero" role="recipient" full="yes">Piero Sraffa</persName>, [3. 4. 1939]</title> <author>Wittgenstein, Ludwig</author> </titleStmt> <editionStmt n="bw2"> <edition>2. Auflage</edition> </editionStmt> <publicationStmt> <p>Ludwig Wittgenstein: Gesamtbriefwechsel, 2. Auflage</p> </publicationStmt> <sourceDesc default="false"> <p>Abschrift McGuinness, Kopie in BA.</p> </sourceDesc> </fileDesc><encodingDesc><p>TEI P5</p></encodingDesc><revisionDesc><list type="simple"><item>2010/05/14: Added to the collection</item><item>2018/12: Added to Innsbruck Correspondence Edition</item></list></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="transcript"> <div type="maintext" org="uniform" sample="complete" part="N"> <p rend="left">Dear Sraffa,</p> <p rend="indent">I should not recommend S., for personal reasons. B &amp; N I don’t know, but perhaps N would be the right man. C I’ve heard of &amp; I’m slightly doubtful. Remember me to your mother. Good wishes!</p> <p rend="indent">Wittgenstein</p> </div> </div></body></text></TEI>